# ─── ORACLE '26 environment ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# The app works with NO env vars at all: the Oracle falls back to the
# deterministic engine. Set the variables below to enable the natural-language
# (LLM) Oracle via the Vercel AI Gateway.

# Vercel AI Gateway key. On Vercel, prefer OIDC (auto-injected VERCEL_OIDC_TOKEN
# via `vercel env pull`) and you can leave this unset. For local LLM testing,
# create a key at: https://vercel.com/[team]/~/ai-gateway/api-keys
AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY=

# Optional: override the Oracle model (routed through the AI Gateway).
# Defaults to anthropic/claude-haiku-4.5 (fast + cheap). List models:
#   curl -s https://ai-gateway.vercel.sh/v1/models | jq -r '.data[].id'
# ORACLE_MODEL=anthropic/claude-haiku-4.5
